{"tid":2017502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家快啲幫手睇「監警會專題審視報告」全文","createTime":"2020-05-15T06:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T09:55:16.000Z","uid":71237,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e878e7613a14904b42e45b5a2de5e2f3c28e70","tid":2017502,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"過千頁PDF的內容記者都唔睇得咁多。<br />\n大家入嚟一齊睇，見到有咩值得留意、遺漏的地方就講出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n1. 監警會專題審視報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/public_communications/ipcc_thematic_study_report.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_communications%2Fipcc_thematic_study_report.html&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=52ec980a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/public_communications/ipcc_thematic_study_report.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 附件<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/public_communications/annexes.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_communications%2Fannexes.html&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=34445f5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/public_communications/annexes.html</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 相關調查研究<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/public_communications/researches.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_communications%2Fresearches.html&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=13dff5aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/public_communications/researches.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e230f841dc62e31e504e30631afe7af3e203a55","tid":2017502,"uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"其中一個資料源係微博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73caaa8ce87a23dcaa22490c9d9c2ae35814f426","tid":2017502,"uid":133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0e230f841dc62e31e504e3