d":"f778052cf515d90550492c483c43f53f0f6f6e8e","tid":2017502,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e230f841dc62e31e504e30631afe7af3e203a55","tid":2017502,"uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"其中一個資料源係微博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"可以進一步睇下有冇factual嘢錯咗，或者有冇咩觀點係特別奇怪嘅。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"講死人好難掩埋唔比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690bc7370d63b6b5a66daf96e7a3c31f9bf45983","tid":2017502,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">JM9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n查831都要用到宇宙學㗎</span></strong></span><br />\n份報告咁低能邊個寫<br />\n<br />\n網上聲稱警方在太子站殺人的消息如何從揣測迅 速升級為傳言，再變成所謂的確認，而在此轉變過程中並無任何事實 依據。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宇宙學家</span>卡爾&middot;薩根(Carl Sagan)因宣揚檢驗超乎尋常的主張 (extraordinary claims)的標準而著稱。相關標準是「超乎尋常的主張 需要有超乎尋常的證據」(Extraordinary Claims Require Extraordinary Evidence)，簡稱 ECREE。當然，這並非甚麼新鮮事物</strong></span>，只是向外行人 描述科學方法的一種方式，所反映的是常識觀念，亦即提出超乎尋常 主張的人需要提出超乎尋常的證據去支持其主張。"},{"pid":"d64dcd2654223af7b4d1e2b30c4f2a2fbf9c496d","tid":2017502,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"怪唔之得要左改右改啦<br />\n原來要度下點讚美警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5f939ead9d041ca55e7c73e23d623aa7746b42","tid":2017502,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n聽你地討論都笑到我癡線<br />\n洗唔洗用埋宇宙相對論黎監察狗仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c672769b6bf74fd545b1eada21b7fb9b447b58","tid":2017502,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"690bc7370d63b6b5a66daf96e7a3c31f9bf45983","tid":2017502,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">JM9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n查831都要用到宇宙學㗎</span></strong></span><br />\n份報告咁低能邊個寫<br />\n<br />\n網上聲稱警方在太子站殺人的消息如何從揣測迅 速升級為傳言，再變成所謂的確認，而在此轉變過程中並無任何事實 依據。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宇宙學家</span>卡爾&middot;薩根(Carl Sagan)因宣揚檢驗超乎尋常的主張 (extraordinary claims)的標準而著稱。相關標準是「超乎尋常的主張 需要有超乎尋常的證據」(Extraordinary Claims Require Extraordinary Evidence)，簡稱 ECREE。當然，這並非甚麼新鮮事物</strong></span>，只是向外行人 描述科學方法的一種方式，所反映的是常識觀念，亦即提出超乎尋常 主張的人需要提出超乎尋常的證據去支持其主張。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718acc9f171a9135ff055a60c99ab9dab8ec171b","tid":2017502,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">市民對7月21日事件的觀感被誤導</span>，包括把元朗站內的事件認定為單方面、無差別的恐怖襲擊，而實際上是當時雙方都有大量參與者進行集體毆鬥引發，  而新界北總區應變大隊人員把南邊圍內外兩批人士分隔開，以及刑事調查人員其後並未即場採取拘捕行動，亦被指控為警方與黑社會勾結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0